      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
