    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. Power is delivered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain with an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains taut, riding on a refined MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. With its original Laguna Seca Blue finish and flawless Nappa leather interior, this E46 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
